<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.9.2">
<l>tarumāṉa maḻaimukilaip piriyā tutaṉṉaṭaintār</l>
<l>varumāṉam tavirkkum maṇiyai yaṇiyuruvil</l>
<l>tirumālai yammāṉai yamutattaik kaṭaṟkiṭanta</l>
<l>perumāṉai yaṭiyē ṉaṭaintuyntu piḻaittēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Taking refuge in the cloud with rain like the wish-giving tree,</l>
<l>The jewel, being inseparable, who removes the faults</l>
<l rend="indent">which come to his adherents</l>
<l>Tirumāl in [his] beautiful form, the lord, nectar,</l>
<l rend="indent">great lord who sleeps in the Sea [of Milk],</l>
<l>I, his servant, being saved, was liberated.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
